    <!-- FAQ -->
    <string name="faq_q1">How does a reading work?</string>
    <string name="faq_a1">Choose a topic, optionally ask a question, select a card spread, and reveal your cards by tapping. Our AI fortune teller Madame Stella will then interpret your cards in the context of your question.</string>
    <string name="faq_q2">Are readings free?</string>
    <string name="faq_a2">You get 3 readings completely free. After that, you can purchase coin packs for additional readings. The daily card is always free.</string>
    <string name="faq_q3">How do coins work?</string>
    <string name="faq_a3">Coins are used to pay for readings. Different spreads cost different amounts: 1 card = 1 coin, 3 cards = 2 coins, Celtic Cross = 3 coins.</string>
    <string name="faq_q4">Is tarot accurate?</string>
    <string name="faq_a4">Tarot is a tool for introspection and personal growth. Readings are generated by AI and serve as inspiration, not as definitive predictions of the future.</string>
    <string name="faq_q5">Can I ask follow-up questions?</string>
    <string name="faq_a5">Yes! After each reading, you can ask Madame Stella anything else about your cards — at no extra cost.</string>
